record.text:
Dear Diary, I have been musing over my packing list for my trip to the wet little village! 
- My toadshark hide boots, for mucking about with the common folk! 
- A photo of Mummy, for my bedside table!
- My best whippoorwill tail quill, for signing royal decrees!
- You, old chum, of course!
